{"tid":2407410,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"Robinhood、Reddit CEO被傳召國會就GME事件作供","createTime":"2021-02-14T04:29:22.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-14T10:45:31.000Z","uid":28765,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"fe0c0d85503e5d13a615b4ff1c8ee186e67fa702","tid":2407410,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T04:29:22.000Z","msg":"遊戲零售商GameStop（GME）早前的沽空大戰，全球矚目，以Robinhood為首的多間證券商因曾停止散戶買入相關股份，引起市場混亂。美國眾議院金融服務委員會將於本月18日就事件舉行聽證會，而有消息指，Robinhood、宣佈撤出沽空市場的Citron、1月狂輸53%的Melvin Capital，他們的CEO都會在聽證會前先作供，而散戶集中的社交平台Reddit CEO亦會提早被傳召作供。<br />\n<br />\n《路透社》報道指，該委員會將仔細查證GameStop等股份如何被大量交投炒起，並導致Melvin Capital等金融機構錄巨額損失。<br />\n<br />\n....<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20210213/RBGHOAYJOBE63K2C64YBR4HHCY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20210213%2FRBGHOAYJOBE63K2C64YBR4HHCY%2F&d=kmAW5qHYNhnz24jV18NLuUYD92OErucUe%2F0sHRi%2FZkY%3D&h=5bb6ff4f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20210213%2FRBGHOAYJOBE63K2C64YBR4HHCY%2F&h=168c4941\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20210213/RBGHOAYJOBE63K2C64YBR4HHCY/</a>"},{"pid":"b601080669b7d479d5de5d5a0325653eaa07b359","tid":2407410,"uid":247064,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T10:18:54.000Z","msg":"散戶可以被割，大戶一蚊都唔輸得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c0f13b2c93d41d2a6e0b91b57c862e88d97ae5f","tid":2407410,"uid":34714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T10:19:41.000Z","msg":"我隻bb<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abdf4ae099d2fbcc2e2edc35b836905b4e9d85f1","tid":2407410,"uid":60563,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"reply